div.div: v0.4 - Public Release Update Started Added playtime tracking Clamped kill contribution between 0 and 1 Armors can now increase ability scores Living Stone Armor defense: 7 -> 9 Crafting stations now go straight to the crafting menu Added monster drops to bestiary Added dungeon resetting every 3 hours Rebalanced vaults Added crafting from vault toggle Added anvil to Blacksmith Added reforges Added some helper methods to Attack Changed some FormattedName calls to use the ItemHolder, not the Item Living Stone sell value: 50 -> 60 Min floors: 7 -> 10 Max floors: 9 -> 12 Added the Deep Woods Added the Demon Statue

v0.3.0 - QoL Update Unavailable attacks still show up Unavailable attacks are now red Combat sidebar no longer shows in main menu Targets now update if the text changes Inputs now update if the text changes The critical hit notification is now orange-red Added number formatting with commas Siderbar now shows # of level ups available Fixed Groundpount typo In some menu, if you can only take 1 item, you no longer have to specify an amount You can now equip armor Possibly fixed XP share Log now updates whenever you take an action or every 10th tick Added level styling through level 100 and edited some of styling Added button to view your vault in the character menu Adjusted consumable stats Added useful descriptions to consumables Added bestiary Now exits containers if empty
